{"tid":295081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果大家記得屈原既唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2017-06-23T12:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T16:43:49.000Z","uid":2641,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81aac95b19550890b1fd246bb206a2fc3484e938","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"端午節岩岩過左冇幾耐，唔知大家仲記唔記得端午節既由來。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，端午節本身係一個好令人悲憤既故事，當年屈原正正因為愛國，而投河自盡，而大家又知唔知屈原投河自盡前講過既幾句說話呢？<br />\n<br />\n當年屈原遊江，不但冇展現出旅遊既高興，仲臉色憔悴，於是有個漁夫去聊佢傾計，其中漁夫問佢：「點解你唔好似其他人一樣，不理手段，追求利益，反而要自己扮清高呢？」<br />\n<br />\n屈原就咁答：「吾聞之，新沐者必彈冠，新浴者必振衣；安能以身之察察，受物之汶汶者乎？」大約意思就係：當人沖完涼一定會整乾淨d衫衫褲褲，咁人又豈能以自己乾淨既身軀，接受世間既污穢？<br />\n<br />\n二千幾年前，一個好簡單既說話，到而加都岩用，無論你係學生又好，在職人士都好，你都唔應該為左個一千幾百，出賣自己既良心，去埋7月1號所謂既愛國集會，愛國從來都唔係問題，請細讀中國古人個份情操，了解佢地對做人既道理，你自自然然識得愛國，講真人生流流長，一千幾百大把機會，大把日子可以搵，真係唔差在一時三刻，相反，人格係一世，出賣自己人格既事真係會令你一世後悔，最後，請大家用君之心，行君之意，三思而行。"},{"pid":"e96f88e57cb2747f0570b07a13a5cbf07eb4c8c6","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"請大家share比d想去既人啦，救得一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a0a27d6088b8fa6cd6fea77915840d29e42349","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a42918061628a02bf4b4312d870abfb121b9ad","tid":295081,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"點解記念屈原？<br />\n因為佢呢種人喺邊個世代都只係少數"},{"pid":"72624fbeefb3bafc8a05e5adf8b69a6189f00bb9","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c0e811e35337a66565a8f4650531e138977a3d","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:12:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解記念屈原？<br />\n因為佢呢種人喺邊個世代都只係少數</blockquote><br />\n所以我地應該要反思，點解過左咁多年都係冇進步，更加要係佢地身上學習個份情操，憑良心做事，其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e56fe54f89cc68d777c2dc1a0e719458a896e1","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0392996c9f3508e35453b7d144f1d67d5df5040","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"請大家唔好再理班仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb8736e0e23e6b84b63d7e32b32188d5cf81efc","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065af42e6a72657b2afb82d4772b07888c8b98b4","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a33010908b8e7a3fe8eee8950f671ff1e8bf32c","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"忠言又冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfea09bccaed73ce1c0734c7cb45e5652ee4c1b","tid":295081,"uid":10689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"皮已正"},{"pid":"692ee341029dab2a5b4fbc4f6bdd316d78ad22fb","tid":295081,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮已正</blockquote><br />\n多謝推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7869dc7d70784b749a6453558292f1dc313725e6","tid":295081,"uid":61788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:05:47.000Z","msg":"人格無價"},{"pid":"814f2f6a58b35c1896b64e6bcd16f74588a5ef44","tid":295081,"uid":79471,"like"